Package: alignWrap
Title: Wrapper Package for Alignment Tools
Version: 0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Dilip", "G", , "igoldlip@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c())
Description: alignWrap is a package which has wrapper functions to use alignment packages such as 'bwa', 'bowtie2', 'STAR' & 'minimap2'. It basically gives a convenient function to call those CLI tools and give the std output. Helpful to handle the sequencing workflow with R in a uniform way.
